https://www.jhipster.tech/installation/


Quick setup
Install Java 8 from the Oracle website.
Install Node.js from the Node.js website (please use an LTS 64-bit version, non-LTS versions are not supported)
NPM is installed with Node.js but you need to upgrade it: npm install -g npm
If you want to use the JHipster Marketplace, install Yeoman: npm install -g yo
Install JHipster: npm install -g generator-jhipster
Now that JHipster is installed, your next step is to create an application
